      public UserDetailsImpl(Long id, String username, String email, String password, Collection<? extends org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority> authorities)
      Constructor to create a UserDetailsImpl object.
      参数:
      id - The user ID.
      username - The username.
      email - The user's email address.
      password - The user's password (ignored during serialization).
      authorities - The collection of authorities assigned to the user.
